data.description: Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a beautiful home with a gorgeous view located in Magnolia Lakes. Enjoy your morning coffee or evening glass of wine with breathtaking sunsets on your uncovered or screen enclosed patio. Home has tile flooring throughout, wooden kitchen cabinets with granite countertops. The den can be used as a 3rd bedroom approx  (12x12) has no closet. An additional windowless room adjacent to the kitchen can be used as an office or playroom. Affordable HOA  includes resort style community amenities, cable, lawn care and on-site management. Very friendly Community with weekly activities for the whole family. Conveniently located in St Lucie West close to shopping, dining, major highways and beaches. Can not close on or before 2/29/24
